highlights.text: “Feels Like Summer” by Childish Gambino is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 101 spots at #97.
“I Love It (& Lil Pump)” by Kanye West and Lil Pump is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #1.
“Closer” by The Chainsmokers and Halsey has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 90 weeks straight.
Eminem has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Lucky You (feat. Joyner Lucas)” is the highest at #3.
